hite-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;font-family:\'Lucida Grande\', Verdana, Lucida, Arial, Helvetica, \'Times New Roman\', 宋体, sans-serif;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、技术规格要求：详见竞争性谈判文件。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;font-family:\'Lucida Grande\', Verdana, Lucida, Arial, Helvetica, \'Times New Roman\', 宋体, sans-serif;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、投标人的资格要求：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;font-family:\'Lucida Grande\', Verdana, Lucida, Arial, Helvetica, \'Times New Roman\', 宋体, sans-serif;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\">5.1&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">凡有能力提供本竞争性谈判文件所述货物及服务、具有独立企业法人资格的境内供货商或制造商、具备政府采购法第二十二条规定条件的均可能成为合格的投标人。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;font-family:\'Lucida Grande\', Verdana, Lucida, Arial, Helvetica, \'Times New Roman\', 宋体, sans-serif;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\">5.2&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">投标人应遵守中国的有关法律、法规和规章的规定。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;color:#333333;font-family:\'Lucida Grande\', Verdana, Lucida, Arial, Helvetica, \'Times New Roman\', 宋体, sans-serif;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;